LSE, TMX Group to Pay $4.11-a-Share Special Dividend After Deal Is Closed

-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 
2011-06-22T17:03:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/tmx-lse-to-pay-holders-c-660-million-in-special-dividends-on-deal-closing.html
TMX Group Inc. (X) , which has agreed to
an acqusition by  London Stock Exchange Group Plc (LSE) , agreed to pay
a special dividend of C$4 a share to its holders after the deal
is closed. LSE holders would get a dividend of 84.1 pence a
share.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
